  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BlockUserController
    This class controls the creation and storing process of BlockedExperimenters sub-collection inside Experiments collection which stores a list of blocked experimenter.
    CommentManager
    CommentManager is a controller class that is primarily focused on retrieving and uploading comment/response data from the Cloud Firestore.
    ConnectionManager
    ConnectionManager checks if the device is connected to internet and if connection actually works
    ExecuteTrialController
    This class controls the execution and storing process of Trials sub-collection inside Experiments collection which stores the current experiment's trials.
    ExperimentManager
    ExperimentManager is a controller class that is primarily focused on retrieving data from the Cloud Firestore.
    GeolocationManager
    GeolocationManager is a singleton controlling the fetching of the user's geolocation.
    PublishingManager
    This class controls publishing an experiment to our Firestore database.
    QRCodeManager
    QRCodeManager is primarily concerned with the handing of String to QR Codes and Codes back to Strings.
    SearchManager
    This class controls searching the database for experiments.
    StatManager
    Testing value check hopefully inner values
    SubscriptionManager
    This class manages how user subscriptions are added and removed from users.
    TrialFetchManager
    This class controls fetching of trials from Cloud Firebase.
    UserManager
    UserManager accesses cloud firebase to retrieve or store new/updated user info data
